  <p><small>Access to the faculty and staff salary record is provided by the <a href="http://quod.lib.umich.edu/e/errwpc/public/3/3/1/3314612.html" class="muted">UM Digital Library Production Service</a></small></p>
  <p><small>The records include all regular faculty and staff who have an 'active' or 'paid leave' appointment. The records do not include graduate students, other student intern appointments and temporary staff appointments.</small></p>
  <p><small>The salary figure is the annualized full-time rate of pay for the period of appointment multiplied by the percentage of each appointment. Not included in this figure are monies that may be received by some University staff, such as: summer teaching and/or summer research, extension teaching, awards for distinguished professors, incentive payments, clinical service, overtime, and temporary administrative differentials.</small></p>
